.TH wrp_obj2forestshape 1 "February 2026" "arma-tools" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
wrp_obj2forestshape \- convert OFP forest objects to GeoJSON polygons
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B wrp_obj2forestshape
.RI [ flags ]
.I input.wrp output.geojson
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B wrp_obj2forestshape
extracts forest blocks from WRP objects, merges adjacent cells, and outputs forest area polygons.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B
--pretty
Pretty-print GeoJSON output.
.TP
.BI "-offset-x " n
X coordinate offset (default 200000).
.TP
.BI "-offset-z " n
Z coordinate offset (default 0).
.TP
.BI "-index " n
Export only one polygon by 0-based index.
.TP
.BR -h , " --help"
Show help.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR wrp_obj2roadnet (1)
